  "tldr": "This is a protocol that contains only technical corrections to the text and figures in the region's economic reports.",
  "lattlast": "<p>This document does not contain any decisions regarding new projects, funding, or operations. Instead, it is a list of minor changes made to the document to correct inaccurate figures and word choices in the financial reports.</p><p>The changes primarily concern how the region&#x27;s economy is presented. They involve technical details within reports on cash flow, income statements, and economic goals for Region Halland.</p><p>Because these are only corrections to existing text, they do not affect the practical services or decisions that the region makes for its citizens.</p>"
